  "symbolic_arc": [
    "Light (burning bush) → Darkness (cloud) → Deeper Darkness (Sinai) → Luminous Darkness (cleft of rock)",
    "This is Gregory's signature theological contribution: the three stages of spiritual ascent",
    "Stage 1: Light — God appears as illumination, dispelling ignorance",
    "Stage 2: Cloud — God transcends sensory knowledge, faith begins",
    "Stage 3: Darkness — God is known by unknowing, apophatic union",
    "This threefold progression maps to Pageau's vertical space: light→air→water→earth but INVERTED",
    "Gregory ascends INTO darkness rather than toward light — the deeper you go, the more unknowable God becomes",
    "This is the 'syntax' for symbolic narrative chains we hypothesized Pageau's vocabulary needed"
  ]
